{"type": "article", "id": 33685, "title": "巴黎世家任命新 CEO，以及，这本滑板圣经值得收藏 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-10-25T02:41:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 3178, "name": "无线耳机"}, {"id": 29398, "name": "Globe"}, {"id": 34256, "name": "滑板圣经"}, {"id": 34257, "name": "Triwa"}, {"id": 34258, "name": "洛杉矶潮牌"}, {"id": 411, "name": "beats"}, {"id": 1548, "name": "开云集团"}, {"id": 3203, "name": "Balenciaga"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 14370, "name": "reebok"}, {"id": 15332, "name": "stampd"}, {"id": 29959, "name": "YNAP"}, {"id": 34259, "name": "Hall of Fame"}, {"id": 34262, "name": "Oh My Cream"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161025093301q7KD6QR3VybCzWM9.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/oh-my-cream-raises-6-5-million-10689476/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>法国化妆品零售商 Oh My Cream 获 650 万美元投资</b></a> |  Oh My Cream 成立于 2012 年，它的网店内有超过 1000 个美容单品，并且在巴黎和普罗旺斯开了五家精品店。Oh My Cream 获得了来自 Otium 资本的 650 万美元投资，这是继它的 170 万美元天使轮投资之后的又一笔投资，将被用于促进公司发展，它计划在下一年开设 20 家店铺。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/merged-yoox-net-a-porter-aims-to-be-as-mobile-as-shoppers\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>YNAP 时尚电商集团要专注于移动端电商</b></a> | 在去年，两大时尚电商 Yoox 和 Net-A-Porter 合并之后，据新的 YNAP 时尚电商集团的首席执行官 Federico Marchetti 所称，该集团计划成为一家专注于移动端电商的公司，YNAP 此前还与 Apple TV 合作，在中东和中国开发电视购物 app。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/balenciaga-appoints-new-ceo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Balenciaga 任命新的 CEO</b></a> | Balenciaga 的母公司开云集团宣布，Cédric Charbit 将出任 Balenciaga 新的 CEO。此前，Charbit 曾为 Saint Laurent 工作。这是开云集团最近的一次人事调动，在上个月，开云集团还把 Hugo Boss 的首席执行官 Dietrich Lahrs 调去了 Bottega Veneta。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>洛杉矶街头潮牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/hall-of-fame-reebok-usa\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hall of Fame 与 Reebok 再度合作</a>，带来了 2016 秋冬季 USA 国旗主题联名系列。无论是单品的设计还是众多街头元素的运用上，Hall of Fame 都将美式街头的精神展现得淋漓尽致，这次与 Reebok  的合作也不例外。这个联名系列以蓝白红的国旗配色为主色调，推出了帽款、tee、训练夹克和运动裤等多款单品。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025093848dm1zRXK8Qu7io5WM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025093900v9reMVfZShFC60Gq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025093910JOxT86b1sZ9vNG7U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>Beats By Dr. Dre 带来了年度<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/beats-by-dr-dre-got-no-strings\" rel=\"nofollow\"> GOT NO STRINGS</a> 企划，推出了一系列全面升级的无线耳机产品。最新 Beats<sup>x</sup> 便采用了 Apple 最新发布的 W1 晶片，配备 Class 1 Bluetooth 蓝牙技术，对于 iOS 10 的用户，可以通过简单的蓝牙连接。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025093920EoKC1G90YSm5erUt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610250939323BkRTromDdg9fxp2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610250939429obuxI6E5WmBPNJS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025093950jp47rOToBzGKaCS6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>visvim 推出了大胆的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/visvim-fbt-trapper-hi-folk\" rel=\"nofollow\"> FBT 全新长筒靴</a>。这款长筒靴的鞋身全部为麂皮面料，结合皮革鞋带，保留了 FBT 鞋款的莫卡辛风格。这款鞋共有三种颜色，售价为 1045 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610250940002x6sMLf41WFihYX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666883\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094009LVRp5rTZsk4xSbfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094018G15krBAqo0nuQOCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666234\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">以简约著称的瑞典手表品牌 <a href=\"https://www.triwa.com/zh_s-cn/page/triwa-x-stampd/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Triwa 与洛杉矶潮牌 Stampd 合作</a>，推出了限量版手表和手镯。其手表在设计上完全采用了哑光黑面，以具有鲜明对比的白色指针搭配有金属蝴蝶扣的黑色尼龙表带，内环的细节上还刻有“时间和我对抗世界 | Stampd 洛杉矶” “TIME AND I AGAINST ANY TWO | STAMPD LOS ANGELES”。手镯的设计则保持一致的极简主义和锐利的设计主题。表面为刷黑金属，尖锐的边缘则采用了抛光处理的黑色金属。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094040e6huJiNXESdB0mDW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.134590\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610250940516eCV4z8YcK9OA0Wu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094100OhXpPWCI2m9o1aDq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.413190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094108MSl3ZOGgXF6yRYUK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016102509411625No8hTzlfiW6bS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>澳大利亚著名滑板品牌 Globe 联手球鞋网站 Sneaker Freaker 推出了一本名为 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/sneaker-freaker-x-globe-unemployable\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unemployable 的纪念套装</a>。这本书由 Jason Boulter 耗时三年撰写，超过 700 页的独家内容里面，涵盖了大量珍贵影像以及上百个滑板界的精选采访，称得上是一本值得珍藏的滑板圣经。此外，随书附赠一双 Chet Thomas IV 滑板鞋款，也使用了相同材质的木盒进行包装。 Unemployable 纪念套装现已登陆北美及欧洲市场。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094130BADjfk8HEurWOo2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094143chfB3oqpjWm2Mn5i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094151IGjMt3PlJWSvD0yH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094153d6LkCOc034KlebQD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094204JRmydBcgCnoiY9jG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094208Sd47sRgvzD3hXaP9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094217WlwqG6k2aR93QyEC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094228BRQeI5Hs8W3Caywr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094235mOysoQzVxInrqUYS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161025094248T6qHzu3rZRshOA0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}